<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<strong><a class="nonexistent" href="./RedNaga">RedNaga</a></strong>: In the description of the Disarm spell it is stated that it should destroy doors since beginning, and start disarming traps at level 10, but instead it disarm traps already at level 1. <p>
Further, in the geomancy spell descriptions (those accessed by pressing SHIFT + the spell letter in the geomancy skill  menu), the Channel Element states that at Earth level 8 the healing from channeling flowers or grass can be projected, but i've not seen this yet (though i'm already at Earth skill 23). 
</p>
<p>
Lastly, for the Geomancy spell "call the elements" the in-game description is right ("it can be projected at level 17"), but the documentation tell instead "at <strong>air</strong> level 17 it can be projected". 
</p>
<p>
<a href="./MassimilianoMarangio">MassimilianoMarangio</a>: Corrected the descriptions without changing the code in ToME 2.3.0. 
</p>
